Description:
Welcome to FIU's No.1 dog walking and social club! 

What we offer: 
1. Weekly social walks (All are welcome- with or without a dog!) 
2. Mingling with like-minded people! 
3. Gorgeous pups!
4. Fantastic casual exercise!
5. Exploring new places! 

We want to make this an epic club, so if you feel or want to contribute, DM!:)

Hey everyone, meet Lady Bug!  A 4 year old chocolate Labrador who has been supporting our club from the start with her brilliant and kind mother @salty.sarah.13 

This lady gets around… 
Lady has swam in both the FIU fountain and the Kissing bridge Lake! 🌊

Aligned with her mums career goals of becoming a marine biologist, Lady also loves 
her hammerhead shark toy named sharky! 

Big love to them both!

Hop into springtime by stretching your legs, breathing some fresh air, having a laugh and letting your dog make some friends! 🐣

We ❤️ you all
